===Verb===
[[Category:Japanese Type 2 Verbs]]
'''いる''' (''iru'')

The kanji form of いる is 居る, but the term is usually written in [[hiragana]] (いる).
# to [[be]], [[exist]]
#:いる is only used for animate objects such as people or animals. [[ある]] (''aru'') is used for inanimate objects.
# ''(preceded by a ''て''-form verb)'' to be (doing)

